sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as "Prologue<br/>(D-1 iters)"
    participant B as "Pipelined body<br/>for i in range(D-1, N)"
    participant E as "Epilogue<br/>(D-1 iters)"

    Note over P: i_pro=0<br/>stage 0 fires:<br/>load(iter=0)
    Note over B: i=1: load(iter=1)<br/>matmul(iter=0)
    Note over B: i=2: load(iter=2)<br/>matmul(iter=1)
    Note over B: ...
    Note over B: i=N-1: load(iter=N-1)<br/>matmul(iter=N-2)
    Note over E: i_epi=0<br/>stage 1 fires:<br/>matmul(iter=N-1)
